Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:57.73,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}たった一度、願ってほしい　奇跡を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:03.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}So we always sing a song of wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:08.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}見つめ合う様な Heart and Heart.
