Comment: 1,0:22:32.67,0:22:34.75,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}We believe like Singing.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.75,0:22:40.22,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}將那份唯一 又不起眼的契機 收藏在心中
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.22,0:22:45.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}你溫柔祈願 願總有一天 能永伴身邊
